<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungle">Jungle</a>的 Josh-Lloyd Watson 共同制作。后者还与乐队一起制作了《What Can I Say After I&#39;m Reason?》。和“夜总会”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="花开|展示和讲述" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7p7n1mdLmsY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>汤姆·奥登 (Tom Odden) 等人也将在新专辑中亮相。与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">全英</a>提名歌手兼作曲家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">C​​MAT</a>合作，后者在唱片中共同创作了两首歌曲，名为“I Like Your Look”和“Why Do I Give You The Worst Of Me?”。</p><p>在其他新闻中，乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blossoms-respond-to-oasis-reunion-tour-support-rumours-3793918">最近回应了他们可能在 2025 年重聚巡演中为 Oasis 开场的传言</a>。</p><p>主唱兼吉他手奥格登和吉他手兼打击乐手多诺万在出现在第四频道的<em>周日早午餐</em>时谈到了这些谣言，并表示：“不。我什至认为他们还没有解决这个问题。没有对话或其他任何事情。我认为他们明年可能会解决这个问题。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blossoms-announce-five-nights-in-manchester-residency-for-november-3794201">Blossoms 宣布 11 月在《曼彻斯特五夜》驻场演出的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
简的成瘾宣布中断并取消巡演“由于佩里·法雷尔的心理健康问题” https://www.nme.com/news/music/janes-addiction-announce-hiatus-and-cancel-tour-due-to-the-mental-health-difficulties-of-perry-farrell-3794215?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=janes-addiction-宣布因佩里-法雷尔的心理健康问题而中断并取消巡演Liberty DunworthMon, 16 Sep 2024 15:50:33 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3794215 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Janes-Addiction@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="佩里·法雷尔 (Perry Farrell) 将于 2024 年 9 月与 Jane&#39;s Addiction 合作演出" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Janes-Addiction@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Janes-Addiction@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Janes-Addiction@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Janes-Addiction@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Janes-Addiction@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Janes-Addiction@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>佩里·法雷尔和戴夫·纳瓦罗在舞台上发生口角之后</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/janes-addiction-announce-hiatus-and-cancel-tour-due-to-the-mental-health-difficulties-of-perry-farrell-3794215">《Jane&#39;s Addiction》宣布“由于佩里·法雷尔 (Perry Farrell) 的心理健康问题”而暂停并取消巡演的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Janes-Addiction@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="佩里·法雷尔 (Perry Farrell) 将于 2024 年 9 月与 Jane&#39;s Addiction 合作演出" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Janes-Addiction@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Janes-Addiction@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Janes-Addiction@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Janes-Addiction@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Janes-Addiction@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Janes-Addiction@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janes-addiction">Jane&#39;s Addiction</a>已确认，由于内部冲突，他们将取消巡演并暂停演出。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/janes-addiction-live-in-london-roundhouse-review-setlist-3759853"><b>Jane&#39;s Addiction 在伦敦现场演出：另类摇滚偶像以爆炸性方式回归英国</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>传奇的洛杉矶另类摇滚乐队最近回归了佩里·法雷尔 (Perry Farrell)、戴夫·纳瓦罗 (Dave Navarro)、斯蒂芬·帕金斯 (Stephen Perkins) 和埃里克·艾弗里 (Eric Avery) 的原始阵容<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/janes-addiction-share-first-new-music-from-original-line-up-in-34-years-with-the-rousing-new-single-imminent-redemption-3777682">，并以单曲《Imminent Redemption》的形式发行了他们 34 年来的首张新音乐</a>。</p><p>然后，他们一起开始了一系列英国演出，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-classic-janes-addiction-line-up-reunite-and-play-new-material-at-intimate-london-gig-3759168">在布什大厅举行的一场亲密的复出演出</a>，然后确认了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/janes-addiction-announce-2024-north-american-tour-with-love-rockets-buy-tickets-3760157">与 Love &amp; Rockets 一起进行美国巡演</a>的细节。</p><p>然而，在波士顿最近的一场演出中，舞台上的紧张气氛开始加剧，导致法雷尔对纳瓦罗大喊大叫， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/perry-farrell-and-dave-navarro-fight-onstage-during-janes-addiction-show-3793683">然后推倒了吉他手，导致演出停止</a>。战斗很快就结束了，灯光熄灭，一群工作人员以及艾弗里试图阻止佩里并将他带下舞台。演出提前结束。</p><p>现在，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/janes-addiction-cancel-show-and-apologise-after-onstage-fight-3793861">取消昨晚在布里奇波特的演出</a>（9 月 15 日）后，乐队与歌迷们分享了一份官方声明，确认巡演的剩余部分已被取消，乐队将立即暂停演出。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_-3ZgDv82v/?utm_source=ig_embed